[%# -*- mode: web; coding: utf-8 -*-
  #################################################################
    Page shown after bad reply is obtained from OAuth site.
    Parameters:
       all described in layout.thtml
  ################################################################# -%]
[% WRAPPER layout.thtml
       title="Unexpected reply" %]

<p class="error">
    Invalid or unknown reply obtained.
</p>
<p>
    If you were redirected here from [% site_name %] after granting
    access to [% app_name %], this means something does not work
    properly.
</p>
<p>
    Please make note of URL shown in the browser (but <b>do not</b> post
    it anywhere as-is â€“ it may contain values which should be treated
    as confidential, mask them before quoting).
</p>
<p>
    Restart app/script and try again, if it still does not work,
    report error to the application author.
</p>

[% END %]
